(2265, 407, 'faq_0_full_answer', 'Clēnera (pronounced <em>Clean-air-uh</em>) was founded in 2013 to develop, to build and to operate renewable-energy production facilities. The founders are Idaho natives and we have offices in Idaho and Arizona. We work with private landowners and with other developers to deliver clean, affordable electrical energy to the power grid for everyone to use.'),
