(253, 1, '2015-04-20 15:12:14', '2015-04-20 21:12:14', 'Clēnera is an end-to-end utility-scale solar development and asset management service provider. The Company relies on the deep solar expertise of its executive team and staff (greater than 50 years combined) to identify the industry’s best projects and then to manage those same projects from pre-construction acquisition through construction and into commercial operations.\r\n\r\nEach Clēnera project is fully equity financed, without debt or other structured financing complications, allowing the speed and flexibility necessary to get through even the most challenging project hurdles. With its unique combination of deep solar expertise and all-equity financing, Clēnera is 100% successful at completing its projects, no matter how large.', 'About', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2015-04-29 08:43:46', '2015-04-29 14:43:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/clenera/?page_id=253', 0, 'page', '', 0),
