(255, 1, '2015-04-20 15:12:28', '2015-04-20 21:12:28', 'On behalf of its investor partners, Clēnera acquires solar PV projects prior to construction readiness, during project development stages when significant permitting, interconnection or engineering activities remain incomplete. Our strong financial backing allows the flexibility required for our expert staff to resolve outstanding development issues, to complete construction, and to deliver operating projects with optimized performance that exceeds expectations for landowners and utility customers alike.', 'Developers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'developers', '', '', '2015-05-05 09:52:42', '2015-05-05 15:52:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/clenera/?page_id=255', 0, 'page', '', 0),
